{"tid":1094812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩強調大規模建設工程千萬不可只側重速度，粗枝大葉","createTime":"2019-04-06T14:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T15:24:52.000Z","uid":5195,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a33f4e915f97734ad73e2bcd174388f0eccce9db","tid":1094812,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"北韓官媒《朝中社》報道，領袖金正恩先後視察元山葛麻海岸旅遊區，以及平安南道陽德郡溫泉旅遊區。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩高度評價，稱工人在冬季也創造世上罕見的建設奇跡，大力推進工程，他尤其非常滿意地說，去年年底視察元山葛麻海岸旅遊區工地時，指出的一些缺點已被糾正，形容藝術上有很大的進步和成熟，令旅遊區變得更漂亮、非常壯觀。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩強調，元山葛麻海岸旅遊區的大規模建設工程，千萬不可只側重速度，粗枝大葉。"},{"pid":"a93426efcb749f9e961a1acda420871d0557feb6","tid":1094812,"uid":18484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"金將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd10bd99a44185bd997992990e8de7b82eccd489","tid":1094812,"uid":46943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"整核彈最緊要有食力"},{"pid":"3ee01cfdda1bf14f7e745f586cd8c06dc627b2c5","tid":1094812,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd10bd99a44185bd997992990e8de7b82eccd489","tid":1094812,"uid":46943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"整核彈最緊要有食力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff2ac12e7232cadda2a69672eea0a1917256132","tid":1094812,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"香港幾時會差過北韓？"},{"pid":"c695b56186c2d4a1bc7de6e3f3d4e454c60c256b","tid":1094812,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cff2ac12e7232cadda2a69672eea0a1917256132","tid":1094812,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:58:14